THE GAME
--------

  'Brikabrak' is a Workbench game where 64 tiles are placed in a
brick pattern instead of a regular grid of tiles. The idea is to
move 2 tiles so 3 or more tiles of the same type are placed next
to each other. To complicate matters a little bit, only those 2
tiles that are placed on either side, horizontally or diagonally,
of the clicked tile will move according to the direction indicated
by arrows that are shown at the right of the game board.

  Try to place as many tiles of the same type together as you can,
but avoid leaving only 1 or 2 tiles of any type on the board...

  Have fun!

